name: Listenify
description: Listenify is the first interactive music platform fully integrated with Web3 technology. While listening to the music you love, you will be able to chat with people you share the same taste with. While you can only talk in chat rooms in the beta version, you will be able to both enjoy 3D music and socialize in the music rooms that support up to 10 people with the VR support that will come with the official version. In addition to these, you will be able to earn income with the safes you earn at the end of the day.
